reviewText: Best Comedy on TV. Wish they had made more of this show.

I've been a fan of Russell Tovey's since BEING HUMAN, and I finally decided to track this show down and watch a few episodes. It's so funny and I see so much of my own relationship in theirs. I just wish the DVDs were available in the US! I really hope the BBC gets around to that soon! I would love nothing more than to throw money at them to own this show and be able to watch it whenever I want.
